Eddie, why are we at this scary looking mansion?
埃迪，我们为什么在这座看起来很吓人的大宅子里？

94
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:45,120
It's like ultra spooky.
它超级阴森。

95
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:46,920
I told you already, Shabby.
我已经告诉过你了，沙比。

96
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:50,140
The owner of the house says there's a ghost haunting his house.
房主说他的房子里有鬼魂出没。

97
00:04:50,140 --> 00:04:53,200
So we have to go in and investigate.
所以我们得进去调查。

98
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:56,240
I don't like this.
我不喜欢这样。

99
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:57,280
Come on, guys.
来吧，伙计们。

100
00:04:57,280 --> 00:04:58,880
Stop being such cowards.
别这么懦弱了。

101
00:04:58,880 --> 00:05:01,480
It's a mystery and an adventure.
这是个谜团和冒险。

102
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:03,680
This place gives me the creeps.
这地方让我毛骨悚然。

103
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:05,320
Seriously, guys.
说真的，伙计们。

104
00:05:05,320 --> 00:05:06,560
Just get out of here.
赶紧离开这里吧。

105
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:10,000
I'm getting goosebumps just being here.
光是待在这里我就起鸡皮疙瘩了。

106
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:15,520
Shabby is a scaredy cat.
沙比是个胆小鬼。

107
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:17,440
That laugh came from this room.
那个笑声是从这个房间传来的。

108
00:05:17,440 --> 00:05:18,840
Let's go and check it out.
我们进去看看。

109
00:05:18,840 --> 00:05:20,920
Look, a ghost.
看，一个鬼魂。

110
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:21,920
Run.
快跑。

111
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:28,120
Okay, so now that we understand all the vocabulary we saw in language takeaway, why don't we
好的，既然我们理解了语言摘录中所有的词汇，不如

