take a look at two phrases now in Fluency Builder.
来看看流利度提升中的两个短语。

113
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:41,600
Well, Shabby said we're at this scary looking mansion.
嗯，沙比说我们在这座看起来很吓人的大宅子里。

114
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:43,040
Scary looking mansion.
看起来很吓人的大宅子。

115
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:44,440
So a scary looking mansion.
所以是一座看起来很吓人的大宅子。

116
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:46,560
Okay, so the mansion looks scary.
好的，所以这座大宅子看起来很吓人。

117
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:48,880
All right, so a mansion is a big house, right?
好的，所以大宅子是大房子，对吧？

118
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:50,600
That looks very scary.
看起来非常吓人。

119
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:57,480
Now this is a really useful and helpful pattern you can use with English.
这是一个非常有用且实用的英语模式。

120
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,480
Something looking.
某物看起来……

121
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,760
So adjective looking.
看起来真够形容词的。

122
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:03,160
Right, so you can say good looking.
对，所以你可以说“好看”。

123
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:08,120
And there's lots of examples, so why don't we hear a few more now.
有很多例子，不如我们现在再听几个。

124
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:09,800
Example one.
例子一。

125
