多好看的狗啊。

132
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,040
Can I pet him?
我能摸摸它吗？

133
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:31,320
All right, great examples, and now we know how we can combine looking with different
好的，很好的例子，现在我们知道如何把“looking”和不同的

134
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:32,320
adjectives.
形容词组合了。

135
00:06:32,320 --> 00:06:35,840
For our next phrase, Shabby said this place gives me the creeps.
对于下一个短语，Shabby 说“这地方让我毛骨悚然”。

136
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:38,480
All right, gives me the creeps.
好的，“让我毛骨悚然”。

137
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:41,200
To give someone the creeps.
让某人毛骨悚然。

138
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:44,100
So if something gives you the creeps.
所以如果某物让你毛骨悚然。

139
00:06:44,100 --> 00:06:48,280
It makes you feel uncomfortable and scared.
它会让你感到不舒服和害怕。

140
00:06:48,280 --> 00:06:49,880
