Come to our website, EnglishPod.com and let us know and we'll see you guys there.
来我们的网站 EnglishPod.com 告诉我们，我们会在那里等你们。

214
00:10:36,080 --> 00:11:03,440
Well, thanks for downloading and goodbye!
好了，感谢下载，再见！
